
# === Declaration code generation ===
#
# Each Deor top-level declaration type has its own file:
#
#   codegen_decl/struct.deor         — `struct Name`
#   codegen_decl/enum.deor           — `enum Name`
#   codegen_decl/shape.deor          — `shape name = list of T` / `func of T to U`
#   codegen_decl/validator_type.deor — `type Name(baseType param)`
#   codegen_decl/function.deor       — `fn RetType name(params)`
#   codegen_decl/raw.deor            — `raw TypeName`
